description:
Four immortal brothers and sisters, consumed in an epic struggle to influence and shape the history of Western civilization. From Moses' challenge to the Pharaoh to the origin of the Grail myth; from the extermination of the Cathars to Nostradamus' travels in Italy; from the Spanish Armada to Napoleon's conquest of Egypt; and finally to the trenches of World War I: a secret occult history of the world told in seven chapters.

Collects The Secret History #1-7.
name: Volume One: From the Dawn of Time to 1917

description:
Past rivalries among the original four Archons must be put aside a fifth unnatural Archon, William of Lecce, tries to either bring the world under his rule or watch as it burns. William's plots and puppets drive the world into the Second World War, and the Archons and their players must risk their lives to stop his plans. Collects books #8-14 of The Secret History.

Collects The Secret History #8-14.
name: Volume Two: From 1918 to 1945
